						               													<description>A solitaire print and play game designed for the 'one full sheet label' board game design contest in December, 2010, temporarily available here: http://boardgamegeek.com/image/879311/amnese?size=original&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player controls a hero who, with their trusted ally and a select array of items, must defend the last Resistance H. Q. from a horde of zombies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn a horde of zombies moves towards Resistance HQ (the player's home base). The player then has a series of actions with which to move about the city and defeat the zombies. If zombies reach Resistance HQ, the game is over. The player wins if they defeat all the attacking zombies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The random setup, different movement of zombies, and the selection of items ensure this is a different game each time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Whilst designed for solitaire play, a cooperative multi-player variant is included in the rulebook, temporarily available here: http://www.mediafire.com/file/l3zaiwifym2dupm/HvZ_rules_1.0.pdf&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
